:["If you are unable to find cardamom pods, replace with 2 teaspoons ground cardamom and omit step 2; add cardamom with sugar in step 3.","This cake has a strong cardamom flavour. If preferred, reduce cardamom pods to 2 teaspoons and proceed as per recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h 35m","12 portions"]}